  "When can I make a payment?": "我什么时间可以付款？",
  "Payments are accepted between 10:00 AM and 11:00 AM IST every day. The page shows a live countdown to the window.": "每日上午 10:00 至上午 11:00 IST 接受付款。页面会显示 live 倒计时。",
  "Is my payment information safe?": "我的支付信息安全吗？",
  "Yes. Payments are processed entirely by the secure Razorpay gateway. We never store your payment credentials.": "安全。支付完全由安全的 Razorpay 网关处理。我们绝不会存储您的支付凭据。",
  "What payment methods are accepted?": "接受哪些付款方式？",
  "Razorpay accepts UPI, Credit/Debit cards, Net Banking, and Wallets. If the system is in mock mode, it bypasses actual processing.": "Razorpay 接受 UPI、信用卡/借记卡、网上银行和电子钱包。如果系统处于模拟模式，它将绕过实际处理。",
  "How does the daily tweet limit work?": "每日推文限制是如何运作的？",
  "Your daily tweet limit resets at midnight IST every day. Free: 1/day · Bronze: 3/day · Gold: 15/day · Platinum: Unlimited.": "您的每日推文限制在每日 IST 午夜重置。免费：1条/天 · 铜牌：3条/天 · 金牌：15条/天 · 白金：无限制。",
  "Will I receive an invoice?": "我会收到发票吗？",
  "Yes! After payment, Razorpay sends an automated receipt, and Twiller updates your account state immediately and sends an email invoice.": "是的！付款后，Razorpay 会发送自动收据，Twiller 将立即更新您的账户状态并发送电子邮件发票。",
