  "I completed payment but my account is still free. Why?": "我完成了付款，但我的账户仍然是免费版。为什么？",
  "Typically, subscription activation is instant. When the payment completes, your account should be upgraded automatically via webhooks. If it failed, submit a Support Ticket with your Payment ID, and our automated trace will activate it for you.": "通常情况下，订阅激活是即时的。当付款完成时，您的账户应该会通过 Webhook 自动升级。如果升级失败，请提交包含您的付款 ID 的支持工单，我们的自动追踪系统将为您激活订阅。",
  "What payment window restrictions are enforced?": "实施了哪些付款窗口限制？",
  "To ensure real-time sandbox clearing, payments are accepted daily between 10:00 AM – 11:00 AM IST. If you submit a checkout request outside this window, it will cancel. Check the live countdown on the Premium plans page for opening hours.": "为确保实时沙盒结算，系统在每日 IST 上午 10:00 – 上午 11:00 之间接受付款。如果您在此窗口外提交结账请求，该请求将被取消。请查看 Premium 计划页面上的实时倒计时以了解营业时间。",
  "How can I cancel my active subscription?": "如何取消我当前生效的订阅？",
  "Twiller subscriptions auto-renew monthly. To prevent future charges, you can request a cancellation at any time. Simply submit a Support Ticket with your Plan Details and Order ID. We will cancel the billing agreement, and you will retain premium benefits until the end of your billing cycle.": "Twiller 订阅按月自动续订。为了防止未来产生费用，您可以随时申请取消。只需提交包含您的计划详情和订单 ID 的支持工单即可。我们将取消计费协议，您将继续享受高级权益，直至当前计费周期结束。",
  "Can I have multiple plans active simultaneously?": "我可以同时启用多个计划吗？",
  "No. To avoid unauthorized double-billing, the system strictly blocks initiating a new plan purchase if you already have an active premium plan that hasn't expired. You must wait until your current plan duration ends.": "不可以。为了避免未经授权的重复计费，如果您已经拥有尚未过期的生效高级计划，系统会严格限制您发起新的计划购买。您必须等待当前计划期限结束。",
  "How does the Sandbox testing simulator work?": "沙盒测试模拟器是如何工作的？",
  "In test mode, you can checkout using test UPI IDs or test card details provided by Razorpay. The emulator acts exactly like a real bank capture, generating an identical secure receipt that registers with our servers.": "在测试模式下，您可以使用 Razorpay 提供的测试 UPI ID 或测试卡信息进行结账。模拟器的运作方式与真实的银行采集完全一致，会生成一个完全相同的安全凭证，并在我们的服务器上注册。",
